    • setArrival

      public void setArrival(Intersection deliveryPt, int orderOfArrival, double minutes)
      Sets the arrival times of delivery points composing a tour after calculating the shortest path
      Parameters:
      deliveryPt - : Intersection corresponding to the delivery point
      orderOfArrival - : number corresponding to the order of arrival in the shortest path
      minutes - : minutes spent by the courier to go from the previous delivery point in the tour to the current delivery point

    • addDelivery

      public Delivery addDelivery(Intersection intersection, LocalDate date, int timeWindow)
      add a delivery to the list of deliveries of a courier.
      Parameters:
      intersection - : intersection where the delivery takes place
      date - : date of the delivery
      timeWindow - : hour of the day when the courier should deliver (he must deliver between timeWindow and timeWindow +1)
